title: Snowboard
description: Artec Novus 154W board w/ Head NX One (white) bindings
comments: Try and sell for more than it's worth. I don't really want it gone, but my need of it is dwindling.

title: Snowboard Helmet
description: Protec snowboard helmet (no in ear speakers)
comments: Try and sell. You won't be using it soon and it might be time to upgrade to something with speakers anyways.

title: Socket Set
comments: I'm on the fence about this one. On the one hand I haven't used it in the 8 years I've had it. On the other hand, it's compact and valuable.
